## Testing the Agent

To manually trigger the workflow:

```bash
# Via GitHub CLI
gh workflow run chief-of-staff.yml --repo rtmendes/knowledge-base-nextra

# Or go to: Actions → Chief of Staff → Run workflow
```

Check the Actions tab for run logs. The briefing should appear in your Notion daily log within 2-3 minutes.

## Troubleshooting

| Issue | Cause | Fix |
|-------|-------|-----|
| No Notion page created | Missing `NOTION_API_TOKEN` or page not shared | Add secret, share page with integration |
| Empty ClickUp data | Missing `CLICKUP_API_TOKEN` | Add secret in repo settings |
| Groq timeout | Rate limit or model unavailable | Check Groq status, retry manually |
| Workflow not running | Cron disabled on forks | Ensure Actions are enabled in repo settings |

